headline: Raymond James upgrades Healthpeak, downgrades Healthcare Realty to Underperform
summary: Investing.com -- Raymond James analysts shifted their outlooks on two major healthcare real estate investment trusts (REITs) in a note on Monday, upgrading Healthpeak Properties to Outperform while downgrading Healthcare Realty Trust to Underperform.
